<br>
Timeless Golems: 90% blue, 10% light blue, Epic Pet CAN solo them, but I throw in one cast of scirocco to speed things up a bit<br>
<br>
Shissar Stalkers: 85% blue, 15% light blue, Epic Pet CAN solo them, but same as above I throw in a cast of scirocco to speed it up a bit.<br>
<br>
So basicly it takes me 15m and pet ends up with 75-80% health each time I kill one of these, these mobs are super easy <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->     <br>
