The experience here is amazing, I've gotten 1 skill point and am 3 bubbles into my second skill point (BTW am using my points on run speed increase skill, its worth it, trust me)<br>
<br>
You will need to have a permanent Enduring Breath item, since this zone is a vacuum.  This makes it a good place to go too, because not many people bother getting an EB item so its usually empty.<br>
<br>
Bad things about this zone? well for one, there is ZERO loot, Golems drop a couple of platinum, and the Shissar drop Polished Snake Scales (no stats), which are probably a quest item<br>
<br>
At lvl 59 am able to single pull blue cons standing right next to each other.<br>
<br>
Shissar Stalkers hit for 121dmg max.<br>
Timeless Golems hit about 115-130dmg max.<br>
<br>
I told Bacris, a guildmate of mine about this place but he left after one day, he just didnt find it &quot;fun&quot; lol<br>
<br>
